  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787260/extras/4af82e221464a6b5f64f3a4c1be7188a.avif?t=1739447064\" width=720 height=80 /></span><br>Universe Balancing Bureau is a mini puzzle game in space<br>where you wire up planetary systems and space stations.<br><br>You're a Balancing Agent of the bureau in charge of doing so.<br>Decide how many planets can be fed with resources from another<br>and make smart use of the space stations provided by the bureau<br>to finish the job at hand.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787260/extras/aac6bf30e458aab481e153042c13f291.avif?t=1739447064\" width=720 height=80 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 campaigns with 4 levels each<br></li><li>1 bonus level straight from the Ludum Dare 38<br></li><li>a secret and very hidden way of creating your own campaigns and levels<br></li><li>absolutely funky music!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787260/extras/4af82e221464a6b5f64f3a4c1be7188a.avif?t=1739447064\" width=720 height=80 /></span><br>Universe Balancing Bureau is a mini puzzle game in space<br>where you wire up planetary systems and space stations.<br><br>You're a Balancing Agent of the bureau in charge of doing so.<br>Decide how many planets can be fed with resources from another<br>and make smart use of the space stations provided by the bureau<br>to finish the job at hand.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787260/extras/aac6bf30e458aab481e153042c13f291.avif?t=1739447064\" width=720 height=80 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 campaigns with 4 levels each<br></li><li>1 bonus level straight from the Ludum Dare 38<br></li><li>a secret and very hidden way of creating your own campaigns and levels<br></li><li>absolutely funky music!</li></ul>",
